
----------------------------------\               /----------------------------------
----------------------------------||== INSTALL ==||---------------------------------- 
----------------------------------/               \----------------------------------

Install the following packages:

  - libv4l-dev
  - libx11-dev
  - libxext-dev
  - libjpeg-dev

Example on ubuntu 16.04:

  $ sudo apt update
  $ sudo apt install libv4l-dev
  $ sudo apt install libx11-dev
  $ sudo apt install libxext-dev
  $ sudo apt install libjpeg-dev
